snippet.title: ✦Fetters of the Past✦ SSR Trailer | Vyn's B-day Event | Tears of Themis | JP DUB
snippet.description:
"A Wish in the Light" Limited-Time Event and Vyn SSR "Fetters of the Past" Available Soon

"Did they perhaps tell you about...the assassination of Count Adell 12 years ago?
I am actually afraid of you knowing everything about me.
Hence, the moment I was allowed to enter the side hall, I already knew that Adell had lost."
The dark shadows of the past quietly dwindle as he is gradually enclosed in warmth...
"I apologize. I did not intend to hide these from you and make you worry."

◆This video shows content under development and does not reflect the final version of the game.
